<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
    <title>礼物投诉</title>

    <script src="~/Scripts/jquery-1.8.2.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/miniui/boot.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/Global.js"></script>


    <style>
        .ub {
            display: flex;
        }

        .ub-ver {
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .ub-as {
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }

        .ub-ac {
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .ub-ac1 {
            justify-content: space-around;
        }

        .ub-ac2 {
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .ub-ac3 {
            justify-content: space-evenly;
        }

        .ub-ae {
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        .ub-ps {
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .ub-pc {
            align-items: center;
        }

        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
        }

        tr {
            text-align: center;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #f9fafd;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 2em;
            padding: 11px;
        }

        table, th, td {
            border: 1px solid #ebeef8;
            padding: 11px 5px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .width {
            max-width: 80px;
        }

        .photo {
            width: 4em;
            height: 4em;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .red {
            color: red;
        }

        .blue {
            color: #32cd32;
        }
          .backlog {
            color: #dcdcdc;
        }
        .top {
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .info {
            border: 1px solid #dcdcdc;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            background-color:#fff;
            border-top-left-radius:.5em;
            border-top-right-radius:.5em;
        }

        img {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .state {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight:bold;
        }

        .time-txt {
            color: #777;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .arrow {
            width: 10em;
            height: 0.8em;
        }

        .gift-img {
           width:45px;
           height:auto;
            
        }

        textarea {
            padding: 6px 6px;
            line-height: 25px;
            border: solid 1px #dcdcdc;
            resize: none;
            outline: none;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .text1 {
            padding: 6px 6px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #333;
            border-left: solid 1px #dcdcdc;
            border-right: solid 1px #dcdcdc;
            background-color:#fff;
        }

        .text2 {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: .3em 0.8em;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1em;
            border:solid 1px #dcdcdc;
          
        }

        .check-btn {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #e92162;
            color: #fff;
            height: 35px;
            font-size: 17px;
            border-bottom-left-radius:.5em;
            border-bottom-right-radius:.5em;
            
        }
        .check-btn2 {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #dfdfdf;
            color: #fff;
            height: 35px;
            font-size: 17px;
            border-bottom-left-radius:.5em;
            border-bottom-right-radius:.5em;
            
        }
         .top2 {
            background-color: #e92162;
            padding: 0 6px;
            height:50px;
            position: fixed;
            top:0;
            width:100%;
            z-index:1;
        }

            .top2 #return {
                width: 2em;
                height: 2em;
                padding: 1em 3em 1em 0;
            }
             .top2 #refresh {
                width: 2.7em;
                height: 2.7em;
               padding: 1em 1em 1em 3em;
            }
            .bottom{
                margin-bottom:30px;
                background-color:#fff;
            }
             body{
                 margin:0;
                  font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, tahoma, arial, sans-serif;
                  background-color:#F0F0F0;
             }
             #form1{
                 padding:8px;
             }
               .line{
                 border-top:1px dashed #F0F0F0;
                 margin:3px 0;
                 
             }
    </style>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        var servUrl_AppData = '@ViewData["servUrl_AppData"]';
        $(function () {
            $.ajax({
                type: "get",
                url: "/Admin1/GetGiftTouSuData",
                // data: { "id": id, "state": state },
                success: function (data) {
                    //console.log(data);
                    var data = JSON.parse(data);
                    var id, state, dtm, photo, nick, comment, amount, gift_time, brife, pics, rst_check;
                    var h = '';
                    var btn = '';
                    for (var i = 0; i < data.length; i++) {
                        id = data[i]["id"];
                        state = data[i]["state"];
                        dtm = data[i]["dtm"];
                        photo = data[i]["photo"];
                        nick = data[i]["nick"];
                        comment = data[i]["comment"];
                        amount = data[i]["amount"];
                        gift_time = data[i]["gift_time"];
                        brife = data[i]["brife"];
                        pics = data[i]["pics"];
                        photo2 = data[i]["photo2"];
                        nick2 = data[i]["nick2"];
                        gift_id = data[i]["gift_id"];
                        rst_check = data[i]["rst_check"];

                        var photo = servUrl_AppData + '/photo/' + photo;
                        var photo2 = servUrl_AppData + '/photo/' + photo2;
                        var gift_img = "http://xhcapp.zhuochuangzb.com/img/chart_gift/" + comment + ".png"

                        

                        if (state == "失败") {
                            state = '<span style="color: red;">' + state + '</span>'
                            btn = '<div class="check-btn2 ub ub-ac ub-pc" id="check"><a style="color:#fff;text-decoration: none;" href="javascript:CheckGiftTouSu(\'' + id + '\')">审核</a></div>'
                        }
                        if (state == "通过") {
                            state = '<span style="color: #32cd32;">' + state + '</span>'
                            btn = '<div class="check-btn2 ub ub-ac ub-pc" id="check"><a style="color:#fff;text-decoration: none;" href="javascript:CheckGiftTouSu(\'' + id + '\')">审核</a></div>'
                        }
                        if (state == "待审核") {
                            state = '<span style="color: #dcdcdc;">' + state + '</span>'
                            btn = '<div class="check-btn ub ub-ac ub-pc" id="check"><a style="color:#fff;text-decoration: none;" href="javascript:CheckGiftTouSu(\'' + id + '\')">审核</a></div>'
                        }


                        h += '<div class="bottom">\
                                <div class="info">\
                                    <div class="ub ub-pc ub-ac2">\
                                        <span class="time-txt">' + dtm + '</span>\
                                        <span class="state">' + state + '</span>\
                                    </div>\
                                    <div class="line" style="margin-bottom:10px;"></div>\
                                     <a class="link" style="text-decoration: none;" href="javascript:LookGiftTouSuDtl(\'' + gift_id + '\')">\
                                    <div class="ub ub-ac2">\
                                        <div class="ub ub-ver ub-pc ub-ac">\
                                               <img src="' + photo+ '" />\
                                            <span style="color:#333">' + nick + '</span>\
                                        </div>\
                                        <div class="ub ub-ver ub-pc ub-ac">\
                                            <div class="ub ub-pc">\
                                                <img class="gift-img" src="' + gift_img + '" />\
                                                <span style="color:#e92162">' + amount + '积分</span>\
                                            </div>\
                                            <img class="arrow" src="http://www.daozhenec.com/img/%E5%8F%B3%E7%AE%AD%E5%A4%B4.e607b529.png" />\
                                            <span style="color:#888">' + gift_time + '</span>\
                                        </div>\
                                        <div class="ub ub-ver ub-pc ub-ac">\
                                            <img src="' + photo2 + '" />\
                                            <span style="color:#333">' + nick2 + '</span>\
                                        </div>\
                                    </div>\
                                </div>\
                               </a>\
                                <div class="text1">' + brife + '</div>\
                                <div id="rst_check" class="text2">' + rst_check + '</div>'+btn+'</div>'
                    }
                    $("#form1").html(h);
                }
            });



            $("#return").bind("click", function () {
                location.href = '/Home/Check_Survey';
            });

            $("#refresh").bind("click", function () {
                location.reload();
            });
           
        });
        function LookGiftTouSuDtl(id) {
            mini.open({
                url: "/Admin1/Gif_TouSuDtl/" + id,
                showMaxButton: false,
                title: "查看详情",
                width: 350,
                height: 600,
                ondestroy: function (action) {

                }
            });
        }
        function CheckGiftTouSu(id) {
            mini.open({
                url: "/Admin1/CheckGiftTouSu/" + id,
                showMaxButton: false,
                title: "审核",
                width: 350,
                height: 300,
                ondestroy: function (action) {
                    if (action == "ok") {
                        location.reload();
                    }
                    else if (action == "cancel") {

                    }
                }
            });
        }


    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main">
        <div class="top2 ub ub-pc ub-ac2">
            <img id="return" src="http://wx2.xhchat.cn/img/%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%AE%AD%E5%A4%B4.93b021b8.png" />
            <img id="refresh" src="~/Images/刷新.png" />
        </div>
        <div style="height:58px;"></div>
        <form id="form1">
            <div>
                <div class="info">
                    <div class="ub ub-ac2">
                        <span class="state">成功</span>
                        <span class="time-txt">2020-12-12 16:27:30</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="ub ub-ac2">
                        <div class="ub ub-ver ub-pc ub-ac">
                            <img src="http://xhcapp.zhuochuangzb.com/photo/photo_girl/1001.jpg" />
                            <span>急急如律令</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="ub ub-ver ub-pc ub-ac">
                            <div class="ub ub-pc">
                                <img class="gift-img" src="http://xhcapp.zhuochuangzb.com/img/chart_gift/%E5%B9%B8%E8%BF%90%E6%98%9F.png" />
                                <span style="color:#e92162">3000积分</span>
                            </div>

                            <img class="arrow" src="http://www.daozhenec.com/img/%E5%8F%B3%E7%AE%AD%E5%A4%B4.e607b529.png" />
                            <span style="color:#888">2020-12-12 16:27:30</span>
                        </div>


                        <div class="ub ub-ver ub-pc ub-ac">
                            <img src="http://xhcapp.zhuochuangzb.com/photo/photo_girl/1001.jpg" />
                            <span>急急如律令</span>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="dtl" class="text1">问他啥礼物又不说，送了又说小，这种套礼物的不管管？</div>
                <div id="rst_check" class="text2">根据提供的投诉证据，无法证明存在【欺诈行为】，后续投诉，请提供更准确的截图证明；此处理意见已通知到礼物双方</div>
                <div class="check-btn ub ub-ac ub-pc" id="check">审核</div>
            </div>
        </form>


    </div>
</body>
</html>
